## Sensor Readings [/sensor/{sensorID}/description/readings]
### get list of reading definitions available from of a sensor [GET]

+ Parameters
    + sensorID (required, string, `550e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655456789`) ... String `id` of the Sensor
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)
   
     + Body
     
            {
                "readings" : [{
                    "id"  : '550e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655456789', 
                    "type" : 'temperature'
                    "minimum" : -100,
                    "maximum": 100,
                    "units"   : "celsius",
                    "precision" : 0.01
                },{
                    "id"  : '550e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655456781', 
                    "type" : 'humidity'
                    "minimum" : 0,
                    "maximum": 100,
                    "units"   : "% Relative Humidity",
                    "precision" : 0.01
                }]
            }

### Adds a reading definition [POST]
Adds a reading to the list

+ Request (application/json)
    
        {
            "id"  : '550e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655456781', 
            "type" : 'humidity'
            "minimum" : 0,
            "maximum": 100,
            "units"   : "% Relative Humidity",
            "precision" : 0.01
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            { 
                "updated":true
            }
           
